# fan-in fixture p18 padding 00 repeated frontend input source map data for gateway Inputs payload compression measurement.
# fan-in fixture p18 padding 01 repeated frontend input source map data for gateway Inputs payload compression measurement.
# fan-in fixture p18 padding 02 repeated frontend input source map data for gateway Inputs payload compression measurement.
# fan-in fixture p18 padding 03 repeated frontend input source map data for gateway Inputs payload compression measurement.
# fan-in fixture p18 padding 04 repeated frontend input source map data for gateway Inputs payload compression measurement.
